<p>But neither Middlesbrough and Hartlepool in the North East, two other authorities officially named as a hotspot by Public Health England, were hit by the tough new measures. </p>

<p>The announcement comes amid fears thousands of students returning to university in the area could cause cases to rise even further. </p>

